---
import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Arvind Sagar, a backend engineer focused on systems, infrastructure, and performance."
  currentPath="/about"
>
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Backend engineer with a focus on systems, infrastructure, and performance.</h1>
    <p>
      Experience across startups, freelance consulting, and enterprise
      environments. Primarily working with Rust, building backend systems that
      are efficient, reliable, and scalable.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="split-section">
    <article class="panel">
      <p class="section-label">Strengths</p>
      <ul class="detail-list">
        <li>Strong systems thinking</li>
        <li>Backend architecture design</li>
        <li>Performance optimization</li>
        <li>Ability to build from scratch</li>
        <li>Comfort across infrastructure, backend, and product boundaries</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="panel prose-panel">
      <p class="section-label">Direction</p>
      <h2>Moving deeper into low-level understanding.</h2>
      <p>
        Currently focusing on operating systems, runtimes, memory behavior, and
        performance engineering.
      </p>
      <p>
        The goal is to build backend systems that are not just functional, but
        efficient and well-architected at a fundamental level.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
